    <h1>When Is the Best Month to Climb Kilimanjaro?</h1>
    <p>Honest month-by-month guide to climbing Kilimanjaro: dry seasons, long rains, crowds, sunrise visibility, temperatures, and which months Nelson recommends for which kind of climber.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <span>By <a href="/about">Nelson Mushi</a></span>
      <span>&middot; 2026-06-14</span>
      <span>&middot; <a href="/blog">Back to Blog</a></span>
